damardan gan akmagy ha&yacute;allanda &yacute;a-da petiklenende, gan
be&yacute;leki organlara (a&#351;gazan, gyzyl&ouml;dege) ga&yacute;dyp
gel&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Pressureokarlanan basy&#351; damarlardan
&yacute;arylyp, gan akyp biler.&nbsp;Gemorro&yacute;dan &yacute;okarky
a&#351;gazanda &yacute;a-da &ouml;zofagusda gan akma, derrew lukman&ccedil;ylyk
k&ouml;megini talap ed&yacute;&auml;n durmu&#351; &uuml;&ccedil;in howply
&yacute;agda&yacute; bolup biler.</span></p>

